dct_title_s: Plano de la Ciudad de Mexico
dct_description_sm: North Decimal Degree 19.600000. South Decimal Degree 19.050000. East Decimal Degree -98.950000. West Decimal Degree -99.357500. Inset map: "Distrito Federal." Universidad Nacional Autonoma de Mexico (UNAM) buildings are listed and located. Some buildings are shown pictorially. Administrative boundaries, postal zones and subway project progress are indicated. Map is in two sheets (glued to form one.)
